OPTO TECH CORP said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 18.04% to NT$534,514,000 from NT$652,203,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            534,514          652,203    
YOY%             -18.04%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,168,146        3,798,063   
YOY%             -16.59% 
=================================================================
 